  <ResearchProjectDef>
    <defName>EC_TerraseedEssentials</defName>
    <label>Terraseed Essentials</label>
    <description>Learn how to properly create and grow Terraseeds; specialized seeds that are used to grow biotic gear and equipment, instead of food or materials.
Teaches you how to nurture a Terraforge channeling seed, which can be done at a proper designated spot.
Terraseeds are believed to be divine gifts to the tribes of the galaxy; therefore, it's knowledge is both sacred, and closely guarded. Replicating their secrets as outsiders is indeed possible, but requires excessive effort.</description>
    <baseCost>1750</baseCost>
    <techLevel>Neolithic</techLevel>
    <tab>EC_EcotechTab</tab>
    <prerequisites>
      <li>TreeSowing</li>
    </prerequisites>
    <tags>
      <li>TribalStart</li>
    </tags>
    <requiredResearchBuilding>EC_BasicResearchBench</requiredResearchBuilding>
    <researchViewX>0.00</researchViewX>
    <researchViewY>0.00</researchViewY>
  </ResearchProjectDef>

