  <ResearchProjectDef>
    <defName>EC_RoyalSeeds</defName>
    <label>Lore Entry: Psychic Weaponry</label>
    <description>Records tell of a special, exclusive breed of Terraweapons that only the highest of societies and engineers know of. This research will provide additional information about this unique breed....
\n\nUpon researching, you will discover some information about possibilities known to exist, but not known to the Rimworld. This research currently doesn't grant anything; however, should it's contained knowledge ever come within reach, this information will help you achieve it quickly.</description>
    <baseCost>4000</baseCost>
    <techLevel>Neolithic</techLevel>
    <tab>EC_EcotechTab</tab>
    <requiredResearchBuilding>EC_BasicResearchBench</requiredResearchBuilding>
  <researchViewX>0.00</researchViewX>
  <researchViewY>2.00</researchViewY>
    <discoveredLetterTitle>Secrets of Ecotech: Royal Seeds</discoveredLetterTitle>
    <discoveredLetterText>You have discovered that Prima Terraweapons are just one of several known types of Terraseeds. This particular research has unveiled that one of the most powerful types are known as "Royal" Terraseeds, and are carefully engineered with the mysterious - and massive - power of Anima. Products of these seeds are documented to take up to years to grow, and properly growing them requires skill that only prodigies can achieve; however, any given Royal Terraweapon contains power that rivals - or even completely overshadows - Spacer tech that's widely believed to be superior. The secrets behind producing the weapons are currently lost and not known to any; however, records rumor that *very* few surviving Anima weapons may still be out there, perhaps within relative reach....</discoveredLetterText>
  </ResearchProjectDef>

